snippet.description:
It's been a while since we shared music by Beethoven, so we're truly happy to bring you this peaceful selection for quiet moments.

This compilation includes some of his most beloved works: F√ºr Elise, the Moonlight Sonata, and excerpts from the Pathetique Sonata, all played slowly and gently.

Perfect for helping little ones fall asleep, for winding down at night, or simply enjoying a moment of calm.

Thank you for letting this music be part of your day :)
